Date: 1998-06-29

Title: A relativistically covariant stochastic model for systems with a

fluctuating number of particlesAuthors: L. M. Morato and L. Viola

Comments: 5 Pages; no figures; Plain REVTeX style. To be published in Phys.

Lett. AJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. A246 (1998) 214-218

We construct a relativistically covariant stochastic model for systems ofnon-interacting spinless particles whose number undergoes random fluctuations.The model is compared with the canonical quantization of the free scalar fieldin the limit of infinite volume.